    dc:description "FIGURES 3 ­ 13: 3: General appearance of Dilophotes berezowskii; 4: Antenna of D. lizipingensis sp. n.; 5: Basal antennomeres ­ D. atricollis; 6 ­ 8: Pronota. 6: D. moxiensis sp. n.; 7: D. lizipingensis sp. n.; 8: D. berezowskii; 9 ­ 13: Male and female genitalia. 9: D. berezowskii; 10: D. berezowskii; 11: D. atrorufus sp. n.; 12: D. bhutanensis sp. n., apical part of phallus and internal sac: up ­ upper plate, lp ­ lower plate, br ­ basal rods, ph ­ phallus; 13: D. holzschuhi sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155979/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155980>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 ­ 23: 14 ­ 23: Male and female genitalia: 14: Dilophotes laosensis sp. n.; 15: D. sausai sp. n.; 16: D. bolavensis sp. n.; 17: D. jendeki sp. n.; 18: D. moxiensis sp. n., ar ­ apical ring; 19: D. moxiensis sp. n.; 20: D. pacholatkoi sp. n.; 21: D. pacholatkoi sp. n.; 22: D. anthracinus sp. n.; 23: D. lizipingensis sp. n." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155980/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

